longBusinessSummary: Evolution Blockchain Group Inc. designs, develops, and manufactures engineered fabric and performance technologies. Its fabrics are used in a range of applications in various clothing and textile categories, including sports apparel, medical, sleepwear, linens, undergarments, military, designer wear, protective, industrial, and first responders. The company was formerly known as Garmatex Holdings Ltd. and changed its name to Evolution Blockchain Group Inc. in February 2018. Evolution Blockchain Group Inc. is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
